trans-unit.source: The <see langword="abstract" /> base class representing a field or a property to be extracted from a workflow instance and its associated annotations.

<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract> is the `abstract` base class from which the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> class and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> class are derived.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract> es la clase base `abstract` de la que se derivan las clases <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> y <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> specifies a field or a property to be extracted from the activity associated with a tracking event and a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> specifies a field or a property to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> especifica una propiedad o un campo que se va a extraer de la actividad asociada con un evento de seguimiento y <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> especifica una propiedad o un campo que se va a extraer de la actividad raíz de la instancia de flujo de trabajo.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract" /> class.
When implemented in a derived class, gets the annotations associated with the extracted data.
The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" /> associated with the extracted data.
Annotations are `strings` that you define that contain information to associate with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Las anotaciones son `strings` que define el usuario y que contienen información que se debe asociar a los datos extraídos.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, gets or sets the name of the field or property to be extracted.
The dot delineated name of a field or a property.
trans-unit.target: Nombre delineado con puntos de un campo o una propiedad.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A> can be set to specify a field or a property; a member of a field or a property; or a single element of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A> se puede establecer para especificar un campo o propiedad, un miembro de un campo o propiedad o un elemento único de un campo o propiedad (o un miembro de cualquiera de los dos) que implemente la interfaz <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>.

trans-unit.source: For example, a single element in an `array` may be specified.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, se puede especificar un único elemento en `array`.
